--- !u!114 &1309149414
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1309149413}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 59fce54960a3d2f4db5883e9bc15f078, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  first: {fileID: 1802499019}
  second: {fileID: 1458289617}
  return1:
  - speakerName: Alejandro
    text: Wow.
  - speakerName: Alejandro
    text: I've heard similar from others.
  - speakerName: Alejandro
    text: The rules change every time you come back.
  - speakerName: Alejandro
    text: That is the catch.
  - speakerName: Alejandro
    text: But you keep showing up. That is what matters.
  - speakerName: Alejandro
    text: Wait-
  - speakerName: Alejandro
    text: Again?
  - speakerName: Alejandro
    text: Boy, aren't you lucky.
  - speakerName: Alejandro
    text: To be called back in so soon!
  - speakerName: Alejandro
    text: You've surely made our 5 months together feel like 5 seconds.
  return2:
  - speakerName: Jing
    text: Fourth audition? My, we are long past.
  - speakerName: Jing
    text: I am on my 9th attempt.
  - speakerName: Jing
    text: How long has it been since we've last chat?
  - speakerName: Jing
    text: I wonder...
  - speakerName: Jing
    text: Regardless,
  - speakerName: Jing
    text: These auditions...
  - speakerName: Jing
    text: They're never about the music, are they?
  - speakerName: Jing
    text: Because even when you pass,
  - speakerName: Jing
    text: You'll be stuck proving yourself for eternity.
  - speakerName: Jing
    text: Oh.
  - speakerName: Jing
    text: It looks like you're up again.
  - speakerName: Jing
    text: Good Luck.
