  openingLines:
  - speakerName: 
    text: The Orchestra accepts only the best.
  - speakerName: 
    text: Or so they say.
  - speakerName: 
    text: You've been practicing your whole life for this.
  - speakerName: 
    text: Dreaming of it for as long as you can remember...
  - speakerName: 
    text: Today is your audition.
  - speakerName: 
    text: Don't mess it up.
